{"tid":485478,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【道德難題】如果香港出現一個好似希特拉既人物","createTime":"2017-12-01T03:45:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-01T12:13:34.000Z","uid":12633,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"07bcea40ffd5ae9fb9388b6ba614172abb33295b","tid":485478,"uid":12633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T03:45:18.000Z","msg":"香港人一路睇住香港淪陷，我地可能係無能為力、亦可能係唔想面對呢個現實、拖得就拖，但無辦法，人性就係咁樣。<br />\n面對眼前既絕望，我突然好似明白點解當年既希特拉會咁成功。<br />\n<br />\n背景：中國既低劣文化完全滲入香港，本地有40%人係支那人；支那人就好似病毒／蝗蟲咁侵佔香港資源；同時香港治安變差、毒販、罪犯因為同警方高層有關係、可以互相私通；香港既自由、法治完全喪失；香港人淪為低端人口。<br />\n<br />\n如果：香港出現一個好似希特拉既人物，佢提出要屠殺我城既中國人，清除瘀血；下一步成立香港軍隊，獨立建國；<br />\n<br />\n無視當中既可行性，如果佢既計劃係必然成功，有幾多人會支持呢位希特拉？"},{"pid":"0a513168de88388335553e2fe023c76183f1ce59","tid":485478,"uid":12633,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T03:47:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-UiXvdG-wq-4/WDrnW2e63mI/AAAAAAAACEA/5zw2BlHDlqw0pSl2Sxrc05SecCF2gBsuQCLcB/s1600/tm1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-UiXvdG-wq-4%2FWDrnW2e63mI%2FAAAAAAAACEA%2F5zw2BlHDlqw0pSl2Sxrc05SecCF2gBsuQCLcB%2Fs1600%2Ftm1.jpg&h=e0111e72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「I'd like to share a revelation I've had during my time here. It came to me when I tried to classify your species. I realized that you're not actually mammals. Every mammal on this planet instinctively develops a natural equilibrium with their surrounding environment, but you humans do not. You move to another area, and you multiply, and you multiply, until every natural resource is consumed. The only way you can survive is to spread to another area. There is another organism on this planet that follows the same pattern. Do you know what it is? A virus. Human beings are a disease, a cancer of this planet. You are a plague, and we are the cure. 」<br />\n- The Matrix"},{"pid":"49fc28135c8eb0b6cd1d7fc7ce8f4986122313f9","tid":485478,"uid":70292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci